ent%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20has%20called%20for%20nuclear%20disarmament%20--%20referring%20to%20the%20CPI(M)%20manifesto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20that%20cannot%20strengthen%20itself%2C%20can%20it%20strengthen%20the%20country%3F%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20manifestoes%20of%20INDI%20alliance%20partners%2C%20a%20number%20of%20dangerous%20promises%20were%20made.%20One%20of%20its%20partner's%20manifesto%20has%20promised%20nuclear%20disarmament%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20should%20have%20nuclear%20weapons%20to%20protect%20our%20country%3B%20those%20saying%20otherwise%20can't%20protect%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20further%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Congress%20saying%20no%20sooner%20the%20son%20of%20a%20poor%20family%20became%20prime%20minister%2C%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20spread%20rumours%20that%20the%20Constitution%20and%20democracy%20were%20in%20danger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BModi%20has%20reached%20here%20due%20to%20the%20Constitution%20scripted%20by%20Babasaheb%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20the%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20Dr%20Ambedkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20always%20insulted%20Dr%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar%2C%20we%20have%20honoured%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20the%20Congress%20never%20recognised%20the%20contribution%20of%20adivasis%20(tribals)%2C%20but%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20honoured%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20the%20Constitution%20given%20by%20Dr%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar%2C%20a%20tribal%20woman%20became%20the%20President%20of%20India%2C%20the%20PM%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20Droupadi%20Murmu's%20election%20to%20the%20country's%20top%20constitutional%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20is%20a%20big%20day%20in%20history%20as%20today%20is%20the%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20Ambedkar%20Ji.%20It%20was%20because%20of%20Babasaheb's%20Constitution%20that%20a%20tribal%20family's%20daughter%20has%20become%20the%20country's%20president%20and%20a%20poor%20woman's%20son%20is%20seeking%20votes%20from%20you%20for%20serving%20you%20for%20the%20third%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20got%20an%20opportunity%20to%20develop%20'Panch%20Teerth'%20associated%20with%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar%2C%20who%20was%20born%20in%20Mhow%20town%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20the%20Congress%2C%20during%20its%20rule%2C%20had%20imposed%20Emergency%20and%20dissolved%20state%20governments%20at%20its%20will.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20the%20royal%20family%20is%20threatening%20that%20if%20Modi%20becomes%20prime%20minister%20for%20the%20third%20time%2C%20the%20country%20would%20be%20up%20in%20flames%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20had%20earlier%20also%20made%20statements%20like%20the%20country%20would%20be%20on%20fire%20if%20the%20Ram%20temple%20was%20built%20and%20Article%20370%20(which%20provided%20special%20status%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir)%20was%20abrogated%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20jealous.%20The%20fire%20has%20engulfed%20their%20heart%20and%20mind.%20They%20are%20not%20jealous%20of%20Modi%20but%20are%20jealous%20of%20the%20love%20of%20the%20140%20crore%20people%20of%20the%20country%20for%20Modi.%20They%20are%20restless%20after%20being%20out%20of%20power%20for%2010%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20(opposition)%20INDI%20alliance%20is%20unable%20to%20decide%20in%20which%20direction%20the%20country%20should%20move%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20slogan%20of%20%26quot%3BPhir%20ek%20baar%2C%20Modi%20sarkar%26quot%3B%20is%20resonating%20across%20the%20country%2C%20the%20PM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BModi%20doesn't%20have%20any%20dream%3B%20your%20dreams%20are%20my%20mission%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%