he's%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20sacrifices%20to%20help%20women%20get%20pregnant.%C2%A0Joe%20Donor%2C%20who%20doesn't%20want%20to%20reveal%20his%20surname%2C%C2%A0revealed%20his%20struggle%20with%20loneliness%20and%20life%20as%20a%20sperm%20donor.%C2%A0According%20to%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2024%2F04%2F12%2Flonely-sperm-donor-sacrificed-love-life-father-180-children-20635975%2F%5C%22%3EMetro%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%2052-year-old%20has%20been%20donating%20sperm%20for%2013%20years%2C%20using%20various%20methods%20including%20natural%20insemination%2C%20partial%20insemination%2C%20and%20artificial%20insemination.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20lifestyle%20choice%20has%20come%20at%20a%20cost%2C%20as%C2%A0he%20can't%20have%20a%20full-time%20job%20or%20maintain%20a%20love%20life.%20''You%20always%20have%20to%20be%20ready%20should%20a%20lady%20suddenly%20ovulate%20%E2%80%93%20%5Bthere's%5D%20no%20time%20for%20romance%2C''%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20his%20journey%20has%20been%20fulfilling%2C%20he%20says%20he%20has%20been%20subject%20to%20cruel%20remarks%2C%20with%20many%20assuming%20that%20he%20is%20into%20it%20only%20for%20sex.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''I%20especially%20feel%20hurt%20when%20my%20critics%20say%20I%20only%20donate%20as%20a%20way%20to%20have%20sex.%20You%20would%20think%20that%2C%20as%20a%20natural%20donor%2C%20I%20would%20be%20in%20the%20saddle%20a%20lot.%20But%20I%20have%20always%20said%20if%20you%20want%20a%20lot%20of%20sexy%20time%2C%20you%20should%20get%20a%20girlfriend%20or%20get%20married%20because%20I%20only%20meet%20women%20once%20or%20twice%20a%20month%20typically.%20Because%20my%20baby%20batter%20is%20extremely%20effective%2C%20if%20I%20am%20lucky%2C%20I%20will%20only%20meet%20the%20lovely%20lady%20once%20or%20twice%20and%20then%20she%20falls%20pregnant%20and%20I%20may%20not%20see%20her%20again%20for%20a%20year%20or%20two%20when%20she%20wants%20a%20second%20child%2C''%20Joe%20told%20What's%20The%20Jam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20dedication%20to%20his%20role%20as%20a%20sperm%20donor%20has%20left%20him%20feeling%20lonely%20and%20deprived%20of%20a%20personal%20love%20life.%20He%20continued%3A%20''It%20can%20be%20quite%20lonely.%20I%20have%20given%20up%20my%20own%20love%20life%20to%20help%20others%20in%20this%20selfless%20way%2C%20and%20even%20on%20those%20rare%20occasions%20where%20there%20is%20brief%20intercourse%2C%20I%20don't%20even%20get%20a%20kiss%20or%20a%20cuddle.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20his%20critics%20as%20''keyboard%20warriors''%2C%20he%20said%2C%20''The%20internet%20has%20a%20way%20of%20dehumanising%20people.%20It's%20very%20easy%20for%20people%20to%20make%20hurtful%20comments%20online%20because%20I%20don't%20seem%20like%20a%20real%20person%20to%20them%2C%20which%20they%20would%20not%20say%20if%20they%20met%20me%20face%20to%20face.%20When%20someone%20sits%20behind%20a%20computer%20screen%20and%20reads%20about%20someone%20else%20who%20appears%20to%20be%20getting%20ahead%2C%20it's%20completely%20normal%20to%20want%20to%20punish%20them%2C%20and%20to%20fire%20off%20a%20salvo%20against%20them.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20admitted%20that%20his%20work%20impacts%20his%20finances.%20''Since%20I%20have%20devoted%20my%20life%20to%20my%20peculiar%20form%20of%20charity%2C%20to%20get%20by%2C%20I%20have%20to%20live%20off%20yellow%20sticker%20sales.%20But%2C%20despite%20just%20squeaking%20by%20financially%2C%20because%20I%20am%20living%20a%20life%20I%20love%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20the%20Admiral%20of%20the%20Humber!%20There%20are%20many%20ways%20to%20be%20rich%20without%20money%20%E2%80%93%20I%20am%20much%20richer%20in%20experiences%2C%20travelling%20all%20over%20the%20world.%20And%20I%20feel%20richer%20by%20playing%20an%20important%20role%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20women%20who%20I%20get%20pregnant%20and%20their%20families%2C%20than%20I%20would%20feel%20working%209%20to%205%20in%20an%20office%2C''%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoe%2C%20who%20has%20been%20dubbed%20'Britain's%20most%20prolific%20dad'%2C%20has%20met%20just%2060%20of%20the%20180%20children%20he%20has%20fathered%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20challenges%2C%20Joe%20remains%20committed%20to%20his%20mission%20of%20helping%20women%20become%20mothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713095340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fe2ik6qdg_uk-sperm-donor_625x300_14_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-sperm-donor-who-fathered-180-children-opens-up-about-his-struggles-it-can-be-quite-lonely-5440046%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22His%20lifestyle%20choice%20has%20come%20at%20a%20cost%2C%20as%20he%20can't%20have%20a%20full-time%20job%20or%20maintain%20a%20love%20life.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-sperm-donor-who-fathered-180-children-opens-up-about-his-struggles-it-can-be-quite-lonely-5440046%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-sperm-donor-who-fathered-180-children-opens-up-about-his-struggles-it-can-be-quite-lonely-5440046%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-sperm-donor-who-fathered-180-children-opens-up-about-his-struggles-it-can-be-quite-lonely-5440046%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cheteshwar%20Pujara%20set%20to%20join%20CSK%20in%20IPL%202024%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713094287000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109288923%2Cimgsize-68932.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fipl%2Ftop-stories%2Fcheteshwar-pujara-set-to-join-chennai-super-kings-in-ipl-2024-star-batters-cryptic-post-leaves-fans-guessing%2Farticleshow%2F109288881.cms%22%2C%22summary%22