men%20and%20Child%20Development%20Minister%20Lakshmi%20Hebbalkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Patil%2C%20the%20former%20BJP%20MLA%2C%20at%20a%20party%20workers'%20meeting%20said%20women's%20support%20for%20the%20BJP%20is%20rising%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20which%20would%20make%20Ms%20Hebbalkar%20of%20the%20Congress%20worry%20a%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Hebbalkar's%20son%20Mrinal%20is%20contesting%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20from%20the%20Belagavi%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHebbalkar%20will%20not%20get%20good%20sleep%20looking%20at%20the%20rising%20support%20of%20women%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20Belagavi.%20It%20will%20also%20be%20difficult%20for%20her%20to%20see%20Ramesh%20Jarkiholi%20campaigning%20there.%20She%20has%20to%20have%20a%20sleeping%20pill%20or%20an%20extra%20peg%20to%20get%20a%20good%20night's%20sleep%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Patil%20said%20at%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jarkiholi%20had%20faced%20a%20huge%20scandal%20in%20March%202021%20after%20local%20news%20channels%20aired%20sexual%20content%20on%20a%20CD%20allegedly%20involving%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Hebbalkar%20in%20a%20video%20statement%20condemned%20the%20former%20BJP%20MLA's%20comments.%20She%20questioned%20whether%20Mr%20Patil's%20comment%20is%20an%20example%20of%20the%20kind%20of%20respect%20the%20BJP%20has%20for%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20shows%20the%20respect%20BJP%20has%20towards%20women.%20This%20is%20the%20hidden%20agenda%20of%20BJP.%20It's%20not%20enough%20if%20you%20chant%20Ram%2C%20%3Cem%3Ebeti%20pachao%2C%20beti%20padhao%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20you%20must%20respect%20women%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Hebbalkar%20shot%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20our%20Hindu%20culture.%20The%20remark%20of%20Sanjay%20Patil%2C%20who%20gives%20speeches%20about%20Hindu%20culture%2C%20is%20a%20disrespect%20not%20just%20to%20me%20but%20to%20all%20the%20women%20of%20the%20state%20and%20the%20nation%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Belagavi