hat%20some%20leaders%20were%20posting%20visuals%20of%20non-vegetarian%20food%20during%20Navratri%20to%20appease%20a%20section%20of%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20eating%20fish%20during%20Navratri.%20What%20message%20do%20you%20want%20to%20send%3F%20You%20eat%20whatever%20you%20want%2C%20fish%2C%20pig%2C%20pigeon%2C%20elephant%20or%20horse.%20What%20is%20the%20need%20to%20show%3F%20This%20is%20only%20for%20votes%2C%20for%20appeasement%20politics.%20They%20think%20people%20of%20a%20particular%20religion%20will%20vote%20for%20them%20because%20of%20this.%20Lalu%20ji%2C%20I%20request%20you%20to%20handle%20such%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said%20at%20a%20party%20meeting%20at%20Bihar's%20Jamui.%20He%20was%20there%20to%20bolster%20support%20for%20Arun%20Bharti%2C%20NDA%20candidate%20and%20LJP%20(Ram%20Vilas)%20leader%20Chirag%20Paswan's%20brother-in-law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Defence%20Minister's%20remarks%20were%20a%20swipe%20at%20Tejashwi%20Yadav's%20recent%20video%20in%20which%20he%20is%20seen%20munching%20on%20fish.%20The%20video%2C%20which%20was%20posted%20after%20Navratri%20began%2C%20sparked%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftejashwi-yadavs-counter-after-video-of-him-eating-fish-sparks-row-5411311%5C%22%3Ea%20massive%20row%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20BJP's%20Giriraj%20Singh%20slammed%20the%20former%20Bihar%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20for%20being%20a%20%26quot%3Bseasonal%20Sanatani%26quot%3B%20and%20accused%20him%20of%20practising%20appeasement%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20responded%20by%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20video%20was%20from%20before%20Navratri.%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20uploaded%20this%20video%20to%20test%20the%20IQ%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20Godi%20media%20followers%20and%20we%20were%20proved%20right%20in%20our%20thinking.%20The%20tweet%20says%20%26quot%3BDinank%26quot%3B%20i.e.%20Date%2C%20but%20what%20do%20the%20poor%20blind%20followers%20know%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3