0Crore%20At%20Deloitte%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBen%20Newton%2C%20a%2030-year-old%20man%20from%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20never%20went%20to%20a%20university.%20However%2C%20as%20luck%20would%20it%2C%20he%20is%20working%20at%20Deloitte%20as%20a%20partner.%20The%20average%20pay%20for%20the%20job%20is%20one%20million%20pounds%20(approximately%20Rs%2010%20crore)%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.co.uk%2Farticle%2Fdeloitte-apprentice-who-joined-at-18-becomes-1-million-a-year-partner-and-he-never-went-to-university-pj3qqglr7%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Sunday%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20His%20journey%20began%2012%20years%20ago%20when%20he%20enrolled%20in%20Deloitte's%20Brightstart%20apprenticeship%20programme.%20Mr%20Newton%20became%20a%20partner%20in%20the%20company%20last%20year%20and%20also%20became%20the%20first%20partner%20from%20Deloitte%20Brightstart's%20apprentice%20programme%20for%20school%20dropouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20the%20outlet%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20grew%20up%20in%20Dorset.%20My%20dad%20left%20school%20at%2016%20and%20was%20a%20soldier%20in%20the%20army.%20My%20mum%20worked%20in%20a%20pub%20and%20then%20a%20travel%20agent.%20It%20was%20an%20upbringing%20far%20removed%20from%20London%20and%20the%20world%20of%20finance.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Newton%20had%20been%20the%20first%20in%20his%20family%20to%20be%20offered%20a%20place%20at%20a%20university.%20He%20had%20received%20an%20acceptance%20letter%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Warwick%20to%20study%20maths%2C%20however%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20join%20Brightstart%20so%20that%20he%20could%20get%20an%20early%20start%20and%20earn%20some%20money.%20At%20present%2C%20he%20is%20working%20as%20an%20auditor%20and%20is%20also%20a%20qualified%20accountant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.deloitte.com%2Fuk%2Fen%2Fpages%2Fcareers%2Farticles%2Ffive-things-that-made-me-ben-newton.html%5C%22%3Eblog%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mr%20Newton%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20got%20a%20place%20at%20Warwick%20University%20to%20study%20maths%2C%20which%20I%20was%20looking%20forward%20to.%20But%20that%20summer%2C%20I%20was%20working%20a%20couple%20of%20jobs%20to%20save%20money%20and%20decided%20to%20research%20grad%20schemes%20to%20work%20out%20what%20I%20might%20want%20to%20do%20after%20uni.%20I%20came%20across%20the%20option%20of%20school-leaver%20schemes%20and%20decided%2C%20for%20good%20practice%2C%20to%20apply%20to%20some%20of%20them%20-%20with%20no%20intention%20of%20deviating%20from%20my%20path.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20landed%20a%20few%20interviews%20and%20one%20of%20them%20was%20from%20Deloitte.%20He%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20knew%20I%20wanted%20a%20similar%20role%20after%20university%20and%20I'm%20a%20bit%20impatient%2C%20so%20I%20took%20the%20job.%20I%20love%20learning%20and%20I%20know%20I'd%20have%20loved%20the%20social%20side%20of%20university%2C%20and%20I%20do%20wonder%20what%20would%20have%20happened%20if%20I%20had%20taken%20that%20route.%20But%20on%20balance%2C%20when%20I%20look%20back%2C%20it%20still%20feels%20like%20the%20right%20decision.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Deloitte%20launched%20the%20Brightstart%20programme%20to%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20individuals%20it%20hired%20and%20provide%20them%20with%20an%20alternative%20to%20attending%20college-%20a%20way%20into%20the%20workforce.%20Finding%20individuals%20who%20might%20not%20want%20to%20attend%20college%20and%20expanding%20the%20talent%20pool%20are%20popular%20topics%2C%20as%20is%20encouraging%20more%20people%20from%20lower%20socioeconomic%20backgrounds%20to%20participate%20in%20professional%20settings.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713084540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fghakh8oo_ben-newton_625x300_14_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fuk-man-never-went-to-college-now-earns-rs-10-crore-at-deloitte-read-his-story-5439260%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20present%2C%20he%20is%20working%20as%20an%20auditor%20and%20is%20also%20a%20qualified%20accountant.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fuk-man-never-went-to-college-now-earns-rs-10-crore-at-deloitte-read-his-story-5439260%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fuk-man-never-went-to-college-now-earns-rs-10-crore-at-deloitte-read-his-story-5439260%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fuk-man-never-went-to-college-now-earns-rs-10-crore-at-deloitte-read-his-story-5439260%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Hardik's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20Selection%2C%20Harsha%20Bhogle's%20Damning%20Verdict%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20all-rounder%2C%20remains%20a%20pillar%20in%20the%20Indian%20team%2C%20especially%20in%20white-ball%20cricket.%20But%2C%20what%20if%20Hardik%20is%20only%20playing%20as%20a%20batter%3F%20Does%20he%20make%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20squad%20in%20that%20case%3F%20Over%20the%20last%20three%20matches%20for%20Mumbai%20Indians%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202024%2C%20Hardik%20has%20only%20bowled%20a%20solitary%20over.%20Against%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20and%20Delhi%20Capitals%2C%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians%20skipper%20chose%20not%20to%20bowl%20at%20all%20and%20went%20for%2013%20runs%20in%20one%20over%20that%20he%20bowled%20against%20RCB.%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fpoints-table%5C%22%3EIPL%202024%20Points%20Table%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20does%20leave%20a%20question%20mark%20on%20the%20faces%20of%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20selectors.%20Hardik%20opened%20the%20bowling%20for%20MI%20in%20the%20first%20few%20games%2C%20bowling%203-4%20overs%20but%20things%20have%20dramatically%20changed%20over%20the%20last%203%20games.%20Many%20even%20wonder%20if%20there's%20an%20injury%20that%20has%20prevented%20Hardik%20from%20snubbing%20bowling%20responsibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20New%20Zealand%20cricketer-turned-commentator%20Simon%20Doull%20even%20said%20that%20he%20strongly%20feels%20that%20an%20injury%20is%20preventing%20Hardik%20from%20bowling%20full%20throttle%20at%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20go%20out%20and%20make%20a%20statement%20by%20opening%20the%20bowling%20in%20game%20no.%201%2C%20and%20suddenly%2C%20you%20are%20not%20required%2C%26quot%3B%20Doull%20said%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.cricbuzz.com%2Fcricket-videos%2F85900%2Fhardik-not-bowling-regularly-will-worry-indian-fans-simon-doull%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECricbuzz%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BHe's%20injured.%20I'm%20telling%20you%20there%20is%20something%20wrong%20with%20him.%20He%20is%20not%20admitting%20it.%20But%20there%20is%20something%20wrong%20with%20him%20for%20sure.%20That%20is%20my%20gut%20feeling%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Kiwi%20commentator%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20situation%2C%20famous%20Indian%20commentator%20Harsha%20Bhogle%20asked%20a%20million-dollar%20question%2C%20if%20Harik%20should%20be%20picked%20in%20India's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20squad%20as%20a%20pure%20batter.%20For%20Harsha%2C%20the%20answer%20remains%20no%20as%20there%20are%20other%20better%20pure%20batters%20in%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Hardik%20is%20not%20bowling%2C%20does%20Hardik%20make%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20squad%3F%26quot%3B%20Bhogle%20questioned%20while%20speaking%20on%20Cricbuzz.%20%26quot%3BIs%20he%20among%20the%20top%20six%20batters%20in%20India%20if%20he%20is%20not%20bowling%3F%20I'm%20not%20totally%20convinced%20of%20that%20because%20if%20he%20is%20not%20bowling%20and%20he%20is%20not%20finishing%20as%20powerfully%2C%20he%20needs%20to%20bat%20up%2C%20where%20all%20the%20competition%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713084300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Ff4jfg41_hardik-pandya-bcci_625x300_14_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fharsha-bhogle-delivers-daming-verdict-on-hardik-pandyas-t20-world-cup-chances-5438510%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hardik%20Pandya%20has%20only%20bowled%20one%20over%20in%20the%20last%20three%20matches.%20Does%20he%20make%20India's%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20squad%20as%20a%20pure%20batter%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei%3A%20Iran's%20Supreme%20Leader%20Who%20Vowed%20'Revenge'%20On%20Israel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIran%20has%20launched%20missiles%20and%20drones%20at%20Israel%20as%20a%20retaliatory%20strike%20for%20a%20Israeli%20strike%20on%20a%20Syrian%20diplomatic%20complex.%20Now%2C%20all%20eyes%20are%20on%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Leader%20of%20Iran.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20Israeli%20strike%20targeted%20Iran's%20embassy%20in%20Damascus%20on%20April%201%2C%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei%20had%20warned%20that%20Israel%20%26quot%3Bmust%20be%20punished%20and%20will%20be%20punished%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAyatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei%20has%20been%20the%20most%20influential%20leader%20in%20the%20country%20since%201989.%20He%20is%20the%20commander-in-chief%20and%20the%20head%20of%20state%2C%20overseeing%20the%20morality%20police%20and%20the%20national%20police.%20Ali%20Khamenei%20also%20administers%20the%20Islamic%20Revolution%20Guard%20Corps%20(IRGC)%2C%20which%20is%20in%20charge%20of%20internal%20security%2C%20and%20its%20volunteer%20branch%2C%20the%20Basij%20Resistance%20Force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20facts%20about%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Ali%20Khamenei%20was%20born%20on%20July%2016%2C%201939%2C%20in%20Mashhad%2C%20a%20Khorasan%20province.%20He%20was%20the%20second%20child%20of%20Islamic%20scholar%20Sayyed%20Javad%20Khamenei%2C%20who%20taught%20his%20family%20members%20to%20lead%20a%20life%20of%20simplicity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Ali%20Khamenei%20Khamenei%20continued%20his%20education%20at%20the%20theological%20seminary%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fshrine-of-imam-reza-in-irans-mashhad-once-visited-by-guru-nanak-4625567%5C%22%3EMashhad%20%3C%2Fa%3Efollowing%20this%20elementary%20school%20education.%20In%20the%20remarkable%20period%20of%20five%20years%2C%20he%20studied%20every%20subject%20covered%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bintermediate%20level%26quot%3B%20curriculum%2C%20including%20logic%2C%20philosophy%2C%20and%20Islamic%20law.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20Beginning%20his%20studies%20in%20advanced%20religion%20at%20Qom%2C%20Ali%20Khamenei%20grew%20up%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20some%20of%20the%20most%20well-known%20Shi%C5%BFi%20professors%20such%20as%20Ruhollah%20Khomeini.%20In%20the%201960s%20and%201970s%2C%20he%20was%20detained%20multiple%20times%20and%20imprisoned%20for%20many%20years%2C%20during%20which%20he%20was%20allegedly%20subjected%20to%20torture%20by%20the%20Savak%20secret%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20After%20being%20set%20free%2C%20he%20began%20teaching%20Islamic%20philosophy%2C%20the%20Prophetic%20Traditions%2C%20and%20the%20interpretations%20of%20the%20Holy%20Quran%20in%20Mashhad%20and%20Tehran.%20The%20revolutionary%20Iranian%20youth%20appreciated%20these%20lessons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A05.%C2%A0After%20a%20brief%20stint%20as%20the%20defense%C2%A0minister%2C%20Ali%20Khamenei%20acted%20as%20the%20supervisor%20of%20the%20Revolutionary%20Guards.%20He%20was%20the%20victim%20of%20an%20attempted%20murder%20attack%20in%201981%20that%20left%20his%20right%20arm%20paralysed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E6.%20Upon%20the%20urging%20of%20revolutionary%20elites%2C%20Ali%20Khamenei%20ran%20for%20the%20presidential%20elections%20in%201981.%20He%20served%20as%20the%20president%20of%20Iran%20from%201981%20to%201989%2C%20during%20which%20the%20Iran-Iraq%20war%20gained%20prominence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E7.%C2%A0Since%201989%2C%20Ali%20Khamenei%20has%20held%20the%20position%20of%20Iran's%20supreme%20leader%2C%20marking%20him%20as%20the%20Middle%20East's%20second%20longest-serving%20autocrat%2C%20following%20Sultan%20Qaboos%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-holds-talks-with-omans-sultan-haitham-bin-tarik-4684405%5C%22%3EOman%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Additionally%2C%20he%20ranks%20as%20the%20second%20longest-serving%20Iranian%20leader%20of%20the%20past%20century%2C%20trailing%20behind%20Shah%20Mohammed%20Reza%20Pahlavi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E8.%20In%20his%20role%20as%20supreme%20leader%2C%20Khamenei%20wields%20constitutional%20authority%20over%20the%20judiciary%2C%20the%20armed%20forces%20as%20well%20as%20the%20elite%20Revolutionary%20Guards%2C%20and%20the%20state-controlled%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713084000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-05%2F254soh38_ayatollah-ali-khamenei-afp_625x300_07_May_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fayatollah-ali-khamenei-irans-supreme-leader-who-vowed-revenge-on-israel-5438969%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Iran%20waged%20a%20drone%20attack%20and%20launched%20missiles%20at%20Israel%20as%20a%20retaliatory%20strike%20for%20a%20Israeli%20strike%20on%20a%20Syrian%20diplomatic%20complex.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fayatollah-ali-khamenei-irans-supreme-leader-who-vowed-revenge-on-israel-5438969%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%