over.%20Khomeini%20effected%20a%20180-degree%20shift%20in%20Tehran's%20engagement%20with%20the%20US%2C%20describing%20it%20as%20the%20Great%20Satan.%20He%20coined%20the%20epithet%2C%20%26quot%3BLittle%20Satan%26quot%3B%20for%20Israel%20for%20its%20backing%20of%20Mohammad%20Reza%20Pahlavi%2C%20the%20last%20monarch%20of%20Iran%2C%20its%20close%20ties%20with%20the%20US%20and%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20tensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20hostilities%20between%20Tehran%20and%20Tel%20Aviv%20increased%2C%20Khomeini%20also%20accused%20Israel%20of%20attempts%20to%20thwart%20Iran's%20nuclear%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20decades%2C%20both%20Tehran%20and%20Tel%20Aviv%20have%20attacked%20each%20other%2C%20but%20have%20denied%20their%20hand%20in%20such%20offensives.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20their%20conflict%20has%20been%20termed%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bshadow%20war%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELebanon%20and%20Syria%20emerged%20as%20two%20battlegrounds%20for%20this%20shadow%20war.%20Iran%20backed%20Hezbollah%2C%20which%20has%20been%20targeting%20Israel%20from%20Lebanese%20soil.%20In%20Syria%2C%20Tehran%20backed%20President%20Bashar%20al-Assad%20as%20Israel%20launched%20airstrikes%20in%20Syrian%20territory.%20Golan%20Heights%2C%20an%20area%20in%20Syria%20occupied%20by%20Israel%20after%20the%201967%20war%2C%20is%20used%20by%20Tel%20Aviv%20for%20its%20attacks%20in%20Syria%20and%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHamas%20Attacks%20Israel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%207%20last%20year%2C%20Hamas%20operatives%20launched%20a%20shock%20attack%20on%20Israel's%20cities%2C%20killing%20over%201%2C200%20people%20and%20taking%20more%20than%20200%20hostages.%20In%20public%20remarks%2C%20Iran%20denied%20any%20role%20in%20the%20Hamas%20offensive%2C%20but%20welcomed%20the%20attack%20on%20Israel%20cities.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20posters%20with%20messages%20such%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20great%20liberation%20has%20begun%26quot%3B%20came%20up%20in%20prominent%20street%20squares%20in%20Tehran.%20Mutliple%20media%20reports%20said%20Iran%20had%20actively%20backed%20Hamas%20operatives%20in%20planning%20and%20executing%20the%20attack%20on%20Israel's%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20October%207%20attacks%20triggered%20a%20brutal%20counterstrike%20from%20Tel%20Aviv%2C%20which%20launched%20an%20all-out%20offensive%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%20According%20to%20UN%20estimates%2C%20more%20than%2033%2C000%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20the%20Israeli%20retaliation%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%20opened%20another%20front%20by%20launching%20a%20volley%20of%20rockets%20at%20Israel%20from%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Trigger%3A%20Damascus%20Strike%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%201%2C%20suspected%20Israeli%20warplanes%20bombed%20Iran's%20embassy%20in%20Syria.%20Tehran%20said%20seven%20military%20advisors%2C%20including%20senior%20commanders%2C%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20attack.%20%26quot%3BWe%20strongly%20condemn%20this%20atrocious%20terrorist%20attack%20that%20targeted%20the%20Iranian%20consulate%20building%20in%20Damascus%20and%20killed%20a%20number%20of%20innocents%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Syrian%20Foreign%20Minister%20Faisal%20Mekdad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20strike%2C%20an%20Israeli%20military%20spokesperson%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20comment%20on%20reports%20in%20the%20foreign%20media.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran's%20UN%20mission%20described%20the%20strike%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bflagrant%20violation%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20Charter%2C%20international%20law%2C%20and%20the%20foundational%20principle%20of%20the%20inviolability%20of%20diplomatic%20and%20consular%20premises.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20urged%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20to%20condemn%20the%20attack%20and%20said%20Tehran%20reserved%20the%20right%20%26quot%3Bto%20take%20a%20decisive%20response%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%2C%20too%2C%20vowed%2